# Data Description:
This folder contains all data used to plot main figures.

# Contents:
mdl_performance.mat: LSTM model simulation performance displayed in figure1a,b.
sequence_list.xlsx: The N2O emission sequence displayed in figure1c.
E_estimation.mat: Estimated N2O emissions during 2000-2020, and daily crop-specific emission in 2020, used for figure2 and figure3.
inventory_emissions_country.xlsx: N2O emissions in EU countries across existing inventories and of our estimation, used for figure4.
Europe_country_0p25deg.tif: EU countries included by our estimation, used for figure4b and c.
ne_10m_admin_0_countries.shp: Used for map plotting.
